flowchart TD
  A[Customer Inquiry] --> B[Quotation]
  B --> C{Quotation Accepted?}
  C -->|Yes| D[Create Sales Order]
  C -->|No| Z[Close]
  D --> E[Check Customer Credit & Balance]
  E --> F{Credit OK?}
  F -->|No| F1[Raise Approval / Hold Order]
  F -->|Yes| G[Check Stock Availability]
  G --> H{In Stock?}
  H -->|Yes| I[Reserve Stock & Create Pick List]
  H -->|No| J[Backorder / Trigger Production / Partial Ship]
  I --> K[Pick & Pack]
  K --> L[Dispatch / Delivery Note]
  L --> M[Generate Invoice]
  M --> N[Send Invoice to Customer]
  N --> O[Receive Payment]
  O --> P[Post AR & GL Entries]
  P --> Q[Close Order]
